  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides properties through which a control that displays hierarchical data communicates with a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingPanel" />.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 Controls that display a header and child items use this interface to provide information to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.VirtualizingPanel>. The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> implement this interface.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
